[u][i]Column B & Row 3:[/i][/u] Mafia Rolecop, Mafia Goon, Town Tracker, Town Doctor, Vanilla Townie x 5
[u][i]Column C & Row 1:[/i][/u] Mafia Goon x 2, Town Cop, Vanilla Townie x 6
